    workflows and validation scripts in this repository), except where
    a file states otherwise

This license does NOT apply to English reference files (typically under
en-US paths or names). Those files are provided solely as translation
reference for contributors. Copyright and other rights in the original
English text remain with the respective upstream mod authors and
projects. tML ES Team does not claim ownership of those files and does
not grant any license to them beyond whatever rights you already have
from the original projects (if any).

If a third-party file is included in this repository, its original
license and copyright notices control for that file.

